body:
Woohoo! It looks like, from the output, is that you have a choice of two apks to install:
`bazel-bin/tensorflow/examples/android/tensorflow_demo_unsigned.apk` or the signed one. To install it on your phone, if memory serves, you need to upload it `adb install bazel-bin/tensorflow/examples/android/tensorflow_demo_unsigned.apk`.
